I tried with application/json headers and couldn&rsquo;t able to verify the Recaptcha V3 token.
I found this content-type is working.
const recaptchaFeedback = await fetch( &#34;https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api/siteverify&#34;, { method: &#34;POST&#34;, headers: { &#34;Content-Type&#34;: &#34;application/x-www-form-urlencoded&#34;, // Correct content type }, body: new URLSearchParams({ secret: RECAPTCHA_SECRET, response: recatatchaToken, }), } );
